{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"70205","heading":"National multimodal cooperative freight research program","label":"70205 National multimodal cooperative freight research program","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/stIX/ch702","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe date of enactment of this section, referred to in subsecs. (a) and (g), is the date of enactment of , which was approved .Pub. L. 117–58Nov. 15, 2021"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Establishment","label":"a .—Establishment","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Not later than 1 year after the date of enactment of this section, the Secretary of Transportation (referred to in this section as the “Secretary”) shall establish and support a national cooperative freight transportation research program.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Administration by National Academy of Sciences.—","label":"b Administration by National Academy of Sciences.—","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":".—In general","label":"1 .—In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall enter into an agreement with the National Academy of Sciences to support and carry out administrative and management activities under the program established under subsection (a).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":".—Advisory committee","label":"2 .—Advisory committee","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fb%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the Department of Transportation and other relevant Federal departments and agencies;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fb%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"State (including the District of Columbia) departments of transportation;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fb%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"units of local government, including public port authorities;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"s