apable of designing, deploying, and operating emerging technologies.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Federal Share.—","label":"e Federal Share.—","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":".—In general","label":"1 .—In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/e/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fe%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Federal share of the cost of an activity carried out under this section shall be up to 100 percent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":".—Use of non-federal funds","label":"2 .—Use of non-federal funds","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/e/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fe%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In addition to using funds made available to carry out this section, the National Academy of Sciences may seek and accept additional funding from public and private entities capable of accepting funding from the Department of Transportation, States, units of local government, nonprofit entities, and the private sector.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"f","heading":".—Authorization of Appropriations","label":"f .—Authorization of Appropriations","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/f","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Ff","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"There is authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary $3,750,000 for each fiscal year to carry out the program established under subsection (a), to remain available until expended.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"g","heading":".—Sunset","label":"g .—Sunset","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205/g","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s70205","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs70205%2Fg","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The program established under subsection (a) shall terminate 5 years after the date of enactment of this section.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
